  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5617828">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5617828/" class="title-link">确实是80年代的奇书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5617828"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/47712928/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u47712928-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/47712928/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">menghanyao</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-10-15"
      class="main-meta">2012-10-15 12:18:35</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5617828_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  说它是奇书，在于书中观点在今日看来都非常刺激，此书竟然能以全译本面貌出版，可见80年代末学术氛围之宽松。对照台湾版，似乎只是把蒋总统整体替换为蒋介石，资料非常详细，值得一读。 值得奇怪的另一点是明明是日本人所著的书，其观点却像是台湾国民党出版物，书中注释很少，...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5617828/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5617828_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5617828_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2277828">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2277828/" class="title-link">这是一本奇书。</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2277828"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/xajh/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u4265174-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/xajh/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">笑傲江湖</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-08-27"
      class="main-meta">2009-08-27 15:41:26</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2277828_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  我们看到了另一个蒋介石，他同样为了中国不遗余力地操劳。但是他在对日关系上的态度实在不敢令人恭维，没有向日本索要战争赔偿。 他在晚年做的一件最闪光的事就是为中国海军大开绿灯，因为他知道，国共两党的问题必竟属于内争，当外敌来的时候，还是会携手一致抵抗侵略的。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2277828_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2277828_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










